=Scenario Loader Command line tool=

Scenario Loader command line tool is a debug tool for scenario, domainObject, fragments, etc.. definitions.


==How to build== 

In order to build run over source code of process-engine-impl:

	mvn package

maven will create in target/ScenarioLoader.exe command-line tool


==How to use==

To get help about command-line arguments, please run ScenarioLoader.exe and see help


==Here a simple example==

Note: subject to change during development

1) create a new folder <FOLDER_NAME> on your system
2) copy ScenarioLoader.exe inside it
3) copy src\test\resources\testEntities\collectiveUrbanMobility folder inside your new folder
4) from command line run:

	ScenarioLoader.exe -d <FOLDER_NAME> -f scenario-test-2user.xml
	
5) for help and syntax, type ScenarioLoader.exe without any commands

